  <title>Arkivum A-Stor Storage Integration</title>
  <description>Use Arkivum&apos;s assured archive service to keep EPrints documents safe and secure for the long-term, with 100% guarantee against data loss.</description>
  <requirements>You will need to ensure the following Perl modules are installed:

IO::Socket::SSL
DateTime::Format::ISO8601

You will need to have an A-Stor appliance set-up and configured on your network and the A-Stor samba share mounted on your ePrints server.

Finally you will need to configure the A-Stor server URL and the storage location (mount point) in the x_arkivum.pl configuration file.
</requirements>
